{"tid":2323033,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有冇人一齊行山6","createTime":"2020-12-12T22:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T10:32:34.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1a95cb1662cce27028b20e37e766854161f982f8","tid":2323033,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:39:16.000Z","msg":"琴日我第一次開團<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有三個型男陪我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過太大霧唔敢行山路<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無上到飛鵝山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係觀景台望一望就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過個feel好正仙境咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔記得影相希望型男入黎補圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我就第一次john人地團<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望行得慢唔會比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者你地睇下有冇人撞岩路線係到討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d8635c164347eefaeb477b9e0e2f7c160392f0","tid":2323033,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:40:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea0dc2a1f18feb7fac2f8351674e83f0f9977145","tid":2323033,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:41:50.000Z","msg":"去緊端記飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169916cd933102b7981e5c95db997dcad39d1329","tid":2323033,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936cb41f75218f54daa01ffaa0e52de15bbe166a","tid":2323033,"uid":218407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T22:47:01.000Z","msg":"想行<img src=\"/assets/faces/do